Cluster details
   ibmcloud ks clusters
   ibmcloud ks cluster get --cluster <cluster name or id>
   ibmcloud ks worker ls --cluster <cluster name or id>
   ibmcloud ks worker get --cluster <cluster name or id> --worker <worker node id>
   ibmcloud ks cluster config <cluster name or id>
   kubectl get nodes -o wide
   kubectl get pods -o wide --all-namespaces
   kubectl get services --all-namespaces
   kubectl get deployments --all-namespaces

Identify which components the customer is asking then follow Troubleshooting cluster components.
https://cloud.ibm.com/docs/containers?topic=containers-cs_sitemap#sitemap_troubleshooting_cluster_components
  Such as ...
  Clusters and worker nodes
  Cluster autoscaler
  Cluster networking
  Logging and monitoring
  Apps and services
  Managed add-ons
  Load balancers
  Ingress
  Persistent storage

